name: Clayton
description: Well, to tell you a little bit about my self. I consider my self to be a Gentleman, a Romantic and a Dependable and Responsible person. I also enjoy learning about different cultures too, I have traveled to 4 countries and I have visited about5States in the USA. And, I enjoy doing lots of different things, but I also enjoy just being at home with that special Lady. And, I am also a Retired Licensed Psychiatric Technician and I live alone, I am financially secure, debt free, and even my house and car are paid off. I live in a nice house and I am a very clean person and I also know how to cook,and I also know how to treat a Lady.
